<p><strong>Conditional Welcome Message</strong>
    echo ‘Welcome ‘.($user[‘is_logged_in’] ? $user[‘first_name’] : ‘Guest’).’!’;</p>

<p><strong>Conditional Items Message</strong>
    echo ‘Your cart contains ‘.$num_items.’ item’.($num_items != 1 ? ‘s’ : ‘’).’.’;</p>

